snippet: DeAndre Daniels had 23 points and a career-high 11 rebounds, Shabazz Napier added 17 points, and visiting Connecticut pulled away from No. 17 Memphis for an 83-73 victory.
abstract: Connecticut pulls away from No 17 Memphis for an 83-73 victory; other college basketball news noted.
